headline: Jacobs to Hold Its Fiscal Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) plans to release its fiscal second quarter 2025 earnings results before market open on Tuesday, May 6, 2025, and will host a conference call at 10:00 a.m. ET, during which management will make a presentation focusing on the company's results and operating trends.

headline: Jacobs Awarded Program Management Contract to Rebuild U.S. Virgin Islands
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was contracted by the Virgin Islands Public Finance Authority to deliver program management services for the "Rebuild USVI" initiative – the U.S. Virgin Island's plan to recover and rebuild following hurricanes Irma and Maria.
